OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fbright end to the day. Then the rest
OL,7,Fof the night wiill be dry with
OL,8,Flengthening clear spells. Some patchy
OL,9,Ffog developing by dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FEarly fog patches clearing,
OL,12,Fthen a dry day with plenty of
OL,13,Fsunshine, but some cloud bubbling up
OL,14,Fin the afternoon. Becoming very warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,17,Fand bright with plenty of sunshine
OL,18,Fduring this period. Very warm in
OL,19,Fgeneral, but cooler at times along the
OL,20,Feast coast.
